both your outfit and personality.
Please, become my hero.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あのなぁ……。
遊びだったら、よそでやってくれねぇか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Look here... if you wanna mess around,
can you go do it somewhere else?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
